zenpad (1.5.0-0ubuntu1) focal; urgency=medium

  * New Feature: Tab switching shortcuts (Ctrl+Tab, Ctrl+Shift+Tab)
  * New Feature: Editor preferences (Right Margin, Brackets, Whitespace, Smart Backspace)
  * New Feature: Man page documentation (man zenpad)
  * Fix: No extra Untitled tab when opening files via command line
  * Fix: Language detection for Go, Rust, Haskell, Lisp, Assembly
  * Fix: Indentation support for Go, Rust, Haskell, Lisp, Assembly
  * Improvement: APT repository auto-cleanup (keeps latest 3 versions)

 -- Jagadish Tripathy <jagadishtripathyforyou@gmail.com>  Mon, 13 Jan 2026 21:58:00 +0530

