zenpad (1.3.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * New Feature: Session Restoration with crash recovery
  * New Feature: Confirmation dialog for restoring unsaved data
  * New Feature: SOC-compatible Log-to-JSON conversion
  * Fix: Uppercase/Lowercase shortcuts not working (#46 related)
  * Fix: Search bar focus - paste now works correctly (#46)
  * Fix: Zoom shortcuts now per-tab instead of global (#47)
  * Fix: Reload confirmation when file has unsaved changes
  * Change: Log-to-JSON keybinding from Ctrl+Alt+L to Ctrl+Shift+E
  * Improvement: Recent files menu limited to 4 items

 -- Jagadish Tripathy <jagadishtripathyforyou@gmail.com>  Thu, 09 Jan 2026 11:57:00 +0530

